snippet.title: BISCUITS HALWA | Delicious Biscuit Recipe Cooking in Village | Sweet Halwa Recipe using Biscuits
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook a halwa recipe using biscuits. Usually, halwa is made with wheat flour, but we use biscuits instead of any flour. This is a very easy snack recipe that everyone can easily cook in minutes.

We add milk, palm jaggery, and some nuts to make the halwa tastier and more traditional.

We taste the warm halwa on a rainy day evening! 

The taste is Delicious!

snippet.title: NaaNaa Hyraanaa | Game Changer | Ram Charan, Kiara | Shreya Ghoshal, Karthik | Thaman S | Shankar
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe 👉 https://bit.ly/Saregama_Telugu

Presenting the much awaited soulful melody, NaaNaa Hyraanaa Song Lyrical Video from Game Changer. Game Changer 2024 Latest Movie Starring Global Star Ram Charan, Kiara Advani, Anjali, Samuthirakani, SJ Surya, Srikanth, Sunil and others. Directed by Shankar. Produced by Dil Raju, Shirish, and SVC – Adityaram, under the banners Sri Venkateswara Creations and Zee Studios. Music composed by Thaman S. 

The melody of the year Naa Naa Hyraanaa is beautifully rendered by Shreya Ghoshal and Karthik, with lyrics penned by Saraswatiputra Ramajogayya Sastry. 

Global Star Ram Charan and Shankar's Game Changer is all set for a grand worldwide release on Jan 10th, 2025 in Telugu, Tamil, and Hindi. #GameChangerOnJAN10

Lyrics:
M: Naanaa hyraanaa priyamaina hyraanaa
Modhalaaye naalona lalanaa neevalanaa

F: Naanaa hyraanaa arudhaina hyraanaa
Nemaleekala pulakinthai naa chempalu nimirenaa

M: Dhaanaadheenaa eevela neelona naalona
Kanivinani kalavarame sumasharamaa

F: Vandhinthalayye naa andham nuvvu naa pakkana unte
Vajramlaa veligaa inkonchem nuvvu naa pakkana unte

M: Veyyinthalayye naa sugunam nuvvu naa pakkana unte
Manchonnavuthunnaa marikonchem nuvvu naa pakkana unte

CHARANAM
F: Epudu lenae-leni vinthalu ipude choosthunnaa
F: Gaganaalannee poolagodugulu bhuvanaalanni paala madugulu

M: Kadhile rangula bhangimalai kanuvindhaayanu pavanamulu
F: Evaru lenae-leni dheevulu neeku naakenaa

M: Romaalanni nedu mana premaku jendaalaaye
F: Aemmaayo mari emo naranaramu nailu nadhaaye

M: Thanuveleni praanaalu thaaraade premallo
Anaganagaa samayamulo tholikathagaaa....

snippet.title: I tested VIRAL Instagram REEL Products!!
snippet.description:
Do viral Instagram reel products actually work, or are they just for show? In today’s video, I tried some weird and hilarious products – like a Maggi straightener, a baby 360 bowl, an electric nail cutter, and even pulled off a funny ghost prank! Oh, and don’t miss the cringe-worthy hairstyles I attempted that will leave you laughing out loud! 😄

Watch the video, have fun, and let me know in the comments which product you found the funniest!

If you enjoy the video, don’t forget to like, share, and subscribe! 💕

-----
Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest. Through the lens of sisterhood's enduring bond and the inexorable force of destiny, the narrative unfurls a tapestry of emotions, ultimately celebrating the timeless allure of fate in uniting kindred spirits.

Star Cast: Deepika Singh, Shubham Dipta, Naman Shaw, Upadhyay Urvashi,Vipul Tyagi

snippet.title: Victory Anthem | Khushi TDT | Lashcurry | Audiocrackerr | Official Lyrical Video
snippet.description:
Thankyou for the crazy response on Victory Anthem! Watch the official lyric video of this banger now and comment your favourite line!

#victoryanthem #khushitdt #lashcurry 

Credits:
Written & performed by- Khushi & Lashcurry
Prod.by - Audiocrackerr
Mix & Mastered by - Xolo

Lyrics:
Hook
Badi Baatcheet Industry Ke Logo Se
Poori Picture Bachi Abhi Promo Dekh
Mere Kisse Sunoge Toh Ro Doge 
Lashcurry Khushi Bakchodi Ni Dono Se
Bhali Bhaati Hume Roka Bhuto Ne 
Parivaar Khush Mujhe Tum Kya Hi Rokoge 
Bistar Bana Denge Noto Kea 
Agar Mehnat Ko Paiso Se Tologe

Khushi's Verse 
Rukegi Kalam Ni Jab Tak Hu Zinda Main
Marungi Tab Tak Ni Kala Hai Zindaa
Mujhe Lagta Hai Jaanti Sab Hu Main
Haar Ya Jeet Ki Hoti Ni Chinta..
Main Sunti Hu Logo Ko Jyada Ni
Par Haa Main Jaanti Sabke Hu Dil Ka
Mere Hote Padosi Ameer Jo Paisa Yaha 
Baatein Banane Se Milta..

Lo Aadat Daal Main Ruku Ye Hoga Ni
Socha Ni Kisi Ni Karungi Sab...
Paiso Se Laakho Ka Bharungi Pet Mein
Mujhe Ni Kamanaa Bharne Ko Ghar 
Phele Bhi Bola Hai Maqsad Ni Hai Mera 
Kamana Paisa Ya Kamana Fame
Faraq Hai Mujhe Badalni Hai Duniya 
Aur Tumhe Badalne Hai Ghar

Karne Se Baatein Hojati Hai Taaza
Wo Yaadein Ki Kaise Kara Maine Shuru Tha Tab
Koi Ni Tha Mere Sath Mein Rone Ko
Aaiyne Mein Baitha Guru Tha Bass
Kehte The Log Tere Baski Ni Tha Mera 
Dil Bhi Naadan Tha Maanta Sach
Par Kuch Ni Hai Aisa Jo Tu Ni Karskti 
Ab Kehta Hai Aaiyna Kehte Hai Sab

Hook
Badi Batcheet Industry Ke Logo Se
Poori Picture Bachi Abhi Promo Dekh
Mere Kisse Sunoge Toh Ro Doge 
Lashcurry Khushi Bakchodi Ni Dono Se
Bhali Bhaati Hume Roka Bhuto Ne 
Parivaar Khush Mujhe Tum Kya Hi Rokoge 
Bistar Bana Denge Noto Ke
Agar Mehnat Ko Paiso Se Tologe

Lashcurry Verse
Sangeet Ko Sab Kiya Samarpit
Likhe Dill Se Gaane Hai Mere Ameer Geet
Bigie Paak Ko Sun Gaya Safar Beet 
Meri Baate Hai Raw No More Color Grid

Meri Maa Se Puchhna Mere Baare Me 
Baap Se Ladi Vo Bete Ko Gaane De
Saath Me Khadi Me Uske Sahare Se 
To Kese Socha Tune Ki Hum Haarenge 

Kitni Dafa Me Gira Kitni Dafa Me Utha 
Kitna Dafa Khuda Me Mujhko Dua Me Suna
Kabhi Ni Ruka Jhuka Ni Kabhi Ni Muda Vuda Me
Kabhi Ni Kisi Ke Baare Kabhi Ni Bola Bura Me 

Damn Mere Aakho Pe Patti Baandh 
Mujhe Dekhna Ni Hate Karu Haq Ki Baat 
Hum Dono Banane Chale Hai Legacy 
Ek Beat Pe Khushi Aur Lashcurry Saath

Hook
Badi Batcheet Industry Ke Logo Se
Poori Picture Bachi Abhi Promo Dekh
Mere Kisse Sunoge Toh Ro Doge 
Lashcurry Khushi Bakchodi Ni Dono Se
Bhali Bhaati Hume Roka Bhuto Ne 
Parivaar Khush Mujhe Tum Kya Hi Rokoge 
Bistar Bana Denge Noto Ke 
Agar Mehnat Ko Paiso Se Tologe

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

snippet.title: Squid Game: Season 2 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Let the new games begin.

Squid Game Season 2 arrives December 26.

Only on Netflix.

More Info on Squid Game Season 2:
Three years after winning Squid Game, Player 456 gave up going to the states and comes back with a new resolution in his mind. Gi-hun once again dives into the mysterious survival game, starting another life-or-death game with new participants gathered to win the prize of 45.6 billion won.

Director Hwang Dong-hyuk, who made history at the 74th Primetime Emmys® becoming the first Asian to win Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series, once again helms the series as director, writer, and producer. Lee Jung-jae, Lee Byung-hun, Wi Ha-jun, and Gong Yoo reprise their roles from Season 1 with an impeccable list of new cast members including Yim Si-wan, Kang Ha-neul, Park Gyu-young, Lee Jin-uk, Park Sung-hoon, Yang Dong-geun, Kang Ae-sim, Lee David, Choi Seung-hyun, Roh Jae-won, Jo Yu-ri, and Won Ji-an rounding out the ensemble of colorful characters in the new season.

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 17 Teaser - 28th November 2024 - Har Pal Geo

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

snippet.title: 1st Test Day 1 | Highlights | England Tour Of New Zealand | 28th November 2024
snippet.description:
England won the toss and elected to bowl first at the start of the 1st test match at Hagley Oval. New Zealand batted for 83 overs and put up a strong total of 319 runs but lost 8 wickets in the process. Williamson was the top scorer with a superb 93-run knock. Day 1 ended with Glenn Phillips and Tim Southee on the crease.

Charnon Ki Saugandh (1988) Part -1 | Mithun Chakraborty, Amrita Singh | Blockbuster Action Movie

"Charnon Ki Saugandh" is a Bollywood movie released in 1988, featuring Mithun Chakraborty in the lead role. Directed by K. Bapaiah, the film falls into the action and drama genres. Here's a brief synopsis of the movie:

The film revolves around the character of Shiva (Mithun Chakraborty), who is a loyal and fearless servant to a wealthy and influential family. He is deeply devoted to the family's elderly matriarch, Thakurain (Nirupa Roy), and her grandson, Shakti (Amrish Puri).

Trouble brews in the household when a cunning and treacherous relative named Sher Singh (Prem Chopra) plots to seize the family's wealth and property. Sher Singh is determined to eliminate Shiva, who stands in his way as a loyal and protective figure.

Amidst a series of dramatic events, Shiva is framed for a crime he did not commit, leading to his arrest and imprisonment. However, his commitment to justice and loyalty to the family remain unwavering.

While in prison, Shiva faces numerous challenges and obstacles, but he never loses hope. He eventually manages to escape and returns to Thakurain's estate to expose Sher Singh's deceitful intentions and bring him to justice.

"Charnon Ki Saugandh" is a story of honor, loyalty, and the battle between good and evil. Mithun Chakraborty's performance as Shiva is a key highlight of the film, and it combines elements of action, drama, and suspense. The movie also explores themes of family values and the resilience of the human spirit in the face of adversity.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4254 - Dunky Wala Tak Kaise Pochenge Jethalal aur Sunder! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide

Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 15 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream - Wahaj Ali - Maya Ali - 27th November 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Man City 3-3 Feyenoord | Haaland (2), Gundogan, Hadj-Moussa, Gimenez, Hancko Goals
snippet.description:
City manager Pep Guardiola said the manner of a dramatic 3-3 Champions League draw at home to Feyenoord was ‘a difficult one to swallow’.

Manchester City lost a three-goal advantage as we were held to a 3-3 draw by Feyenoord in the Champions League.

Erling Haaland struck twice, his first making him the fastest player to 50 goal involvements in Champions League history when he scored from the penalty spot just before the break in just his 44th appearance in the competition.

They came either side of Ilkay Gundogan’s volley for his first goal back at the Etihad Stadium since returning in the summer.

But the Dutch side scored three times in the final 15 minutes through Anis Hadj Moussa, Santiago Gimenez and David Hancko to grab a point.

snippet.description:
चटपटी ब्रेड करंजी, खास तरह का ब्रेड पकौड़ा, जो मिनटों में बने, स्पेशल ब्रेकफास्ट. Spicy and Crispy Bread Karanji for Family Breakfast.

Ingredients for Spicy Bread Karanji
For Stuffing
आलू - Potato - 2 no, boiled
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1/2 tsp, chopped
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 tsp, grated
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 1/4 tsp, crushed
हल्दी - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
अमचूर पाउडर - Dry mango powder - 1/4 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/4 tsp
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1/2 tsp
जीरा पाउडर - Cumin powder - 1/2 tsp, roasted
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 2 tbsp
For Batter
बेसन - Gram flour - 1/2  cup
चावल का आटा - Rice flour - 1/2 cup
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
अजवाइन - Carom seeds - 1/2 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 1/2 tsp, crushed
हल्दी - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
तिल - Sesame - 1 tsp

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Dhiktana Dhiktana - The Hustle Flip l Mad Trip  | MTV Hustle 4
snippet.description:
"This song is a reimagined version of the classic Bollywood track 'Dhiktana Dhiktana', transformed into a melancholic reflection on loneliness and disillusionment. By flipping the upbeat original into a somber tone, the song conveys the harsh reality that no one in this world truly belongs to you. It redefines the familiar melody to evoke a sense of sadness and introspection, making it a poignant commentary on isolation and unfulfilled connections.

Song Credits

Track Name: Dhiktana Dhiktana - The Hustle Flip
Written & Performed By: @MadTrip05 
Music Producer: Aditya Pushkarna
Primary Artist: @MadTrip05 
Track Name: Dhiktana Dhiktana - The Hustle Flip
Singer/Performed By/Cast: @MadTrip05 
Lyricist/Written By: @MadTrip05 
Music Produced By: Aditya Pushkarna
Co-Composer: Aditya Pushkarna
Music Label: Saregama
Genre: Hip Hop
Sub-Genre: Rap
Language:Hindi
Country of Origin/Source: India

👉 Follow us on X: https://x.com/kaanphodmusic?s=11 
👉 Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kaanphodmusic/ 


Lyrics

Mad Trip@MadTrip05 

Kaisa hai tu kaise hain sab 
Poochhe khairiyat par dekhe haisiyat sab
pata chala sirf paison se rishte Hain
toh ab mere sirf paison se rishte hain

Haan maine jeet dekhi 
Haan maine  haar dekhi
Tedha bann ke chalna padta
Warna neki maar degi

Sadkon pe maar dekhi
Apno mein khaar dekhi
Qatl-e-aam ki khabrein Aksar 
qabrein toh aam dekhi

Dekhi saanp Seedhi
Baatein likhun saaf seedhi
Kisi ko bhi Sunn-ni nahi hai
Yahan pe meri aap beeti

Rishton mein rajneeti
Kisse bas jaydaad ke hisse na khaak mili
kishton mein haar mili

Dekhi Kitni shakal gayi pal mein Badal
mere Seene mein kyun hoti Har pal hulchul

Har pal chanchal mann karey bhag-dadd
Ab dil mera khaali Ghar lage khandar

Ghooma nahi main duniya  jahaanon mein kabhi 
Kyun ki pehle se hi maine dekh liya sab shayad
Bura waqt bhi dikha ke jaayega ek Jaadu 
Tu Khaali 10 tak ginn ho jayenge sab gayab

Ae khuda mujhe kya hua
Kyun lagta yeh begaana
Tu bataa main hoon kahan
Manzil ki raah dikhlana

Dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana
Yahan apno mein apna koi dikhta na
Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Saala sacchi mein saccha koi rishta na

Dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana
Yahan apno mein apna koi dikhta na
Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Saala sacchi mein saccha koi rishta na

Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Dhik dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana

Dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana
Dhik dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana

Aansu toh roz aaye par koi na ponchh paaye 
Bolun dil ki baatein par dil tak nahi yeh pahunch paaye
Dhokhe toh bahut khaaye woh toh roz ka hai 
Saare apna soche tu apno ka sochta hai kyun

doon main ghar walon ko dosh jo sochte mera roz
Afsos main unpe bojh main Kosta khud ko bahut
Jailon se bhi zyaada logon ke mann mein hai chor 
woh dekhe kab dheela ho naada 
kab kheenche langot

Jaana kahan soojhta bhi nahi
Ho Bhookhe paet nange paanv 
toh koi thookta bhi nahi
sawaal ka jawaab dene se baney crorepati
Lekin hum jaison ko yahan koi poochhta hi nahi

Bina taane khaaye  milti hain taaliyaan bhi na
Milti kaamyabi toh yeh dekhe khaamiyan bhi na

Kaafi ghalatiyan bhi Kari 
ghalati se seekha bhi main
Yeh duniya ek kitaab toh baatein kitaabi yeh
Chunautiyaan hain log hai kya ismein koi shaq
Roz bolun bhagwan se Enough is enough

Kaash Miley hote gham kam re
Humein bhi koi miley hote humdum re
Ghutt-te hain andar hi andar se
Ab Chubhte hain mujh ko yeh bandh kamre

Main So paaun kabhi chain se
Aise bhi din dikhlana 
Kho jaaunga bheed mein
Tu haath thaam lega na

Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Yahan apno mein apna koi dikhta na
Dhiktana tiktana  dhiktana
Saala sacchi mein saccha koi rishta na

Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Yahan apno mein apna koi dikhta na
Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Saala sacchi mein saccha koi rishta na

Apno ko dekha apno se ladte toh apna hai kaun aaya ek sawaal
Gairon ko dekha maine zakhmon ko bharte toh apna hai kaun phir aaya ek sawaal

snippet.title: കേരളത്തിലെ ഏറ്റവും വലിയ വീട്.... അല്ല, കൊട്ടാരം...!
snippet.description:
കേരളത്തിലെ ഏറ്റവും വലിയ വീട്.... അല്ല, കൊട്ടാരം...! കോഴിക്കോട് പയ്യോളിയിലെ തെനങ്കാലിൽ വീടിന് ഇതിലും ഇണങ്ങുന്നൊരു വിശേഷണമില്ല. നാല് നിലകളിലായി 45000 ചതുരശ്രയടിയാണ് വീടിന്റെ വിസ്തീർണം. അറേബ്യൻ  ശൈലിയുടെ പ്രൗഢിയും മനോഹാരിതയും ഒരേപോലെ ആവാഹിച്ച രൂപം. അതിശയിപ്പിക്കുന്ന വലുപ്പം, കണ്ണഞ്ചിപ്പിക്കുന്ന കാഴ്ചകൾ!ഖത്തർ ആസ്ഥാനമായ പാരിസ് യുണൈറ്റഡ് ഗ്രൂപ്പിന്റെ തലവൻ ഇസ്മായിൽ തെനങ്കാലിൽ ആണ് വീടിന്റെ ഉടമ. കോഴിക്കോട് അമദ് ആർക്കിടെക്ട്സിലെ പി. വി. മുഹമ്മദ് ഷഹീനായിരുന്നു രൂപകൽപനയും നിർമാണ മേൽനോട്ടവും.  2018 ൽ ആരംഭിച്ച വീടുപണി 2024 ലാണ് പൂർത്തിയായത്. 
വിശദമായ ഫീച്ചർ 2024 ഡിസംബർ ലക്കം വനിത വീട് മാഗസിനിൽ....

കേരളത്തിലെ ഏറ്റവും വലിയ വീട്.... അല്ല, കൊട്ടാരം...! കോഴിക്കോട് പയ്യോളിയിലെ തെനങ്കാലിൽ വീടിന് ഇതിലും ഇണങ്ങുന്നൊരു വിശേഷണമില്ല. നാല് നിലകളിലായി 45000 ചതുരശ്രയടിയാണ് വീടിന്റെ വിസ്തീർണം. അറേബ്യൻ  ശൈലിയുടെ പ്രൗഢിയും മനോഹാരിതയും ഒരേപോലെ ആവാഹിച്ച രൂപം. അതിശയിപ്പിക്കുന്ന വലുപ്പം, കണ്ണഞ്ചിപ്പിക്കുന്ന കാഴ്ചകൾ!ഖത്തർ ആസ്ഥാനമായ പാരിസ് യുണൈറ്റഡ് ഗ്രൂപ്പിന്റെ തലവൻ ഇസ്മായിൽ തെനങ്കാലിൽ ആണ് വീടിന്റെ ഉടമ. കോഴിക്കോട് അമദ് ആർക്കിടെക്ട്സിലെ പി. വി. മുഹമ്മദ് ഷഹീനായിരുന്നു രൂപകൽപനയും നിർമാണ മേൽനോട്ടവും.  2018 ൽ ആരംഭിച്ച വീടുപണി 2024 ലാണ് പൂർത്തിയായത്. 
വിശദമായ ഫീച്ചർ 2024 ഡിസംബർ ലക്കം വനിത വീട് മാഗസിനിൽ....

snippet.description:
IPL 2025 Mega Auction Tamil| Updated Squad List of teams Day 2|CSK MI RCB RR DC PBKS KKR SRH LSG GT

#ipl #ipl2025 #iplauction

IPL 2025 Auction Day 1: Franchises spend Rs 467.95 Cr for 72 players, Rishabh Pant most expensive
ndian players stole the show with Rishabh Pant, Shreyas Iyer and Venkatesh Iyer bagging the most money on Day 1.
IPL 2025 auction Day 1: Out of 577 players on the short list, only 72 players were sold. However, out of Rs 641. 5 Cr, teams already spent Rs 467.95 Cr on Day 1, leaving just Rs 173.55 Crore on the table for 132 players on Day 2. On Day 1, Indians were the top picks. Lucknow Super Giants broke the bank, splashing Rs 27 Crore for Rishabh Pant. Minutes before that, Punjab Kings bagged Shreyas Iyer for Rs 26.75 Cr. Kolkata Knight Riders made Venkatesh Iyer the third most expensive player at Rs 23.75 Cr.
Punjab Kings who came to the auction with Rs 110.5 Cr spent the most. They splashed 88.0 Cr for 10 players. Royal Challengers Bengaluru are left with the most purse on Day 2 with 30.65 Cr. Sunrisers Hyderabad will be a mute spectator on Day 2 as they are left with just Rs 5.15 Cr.

snippet.title: Pennine ishtayo? | 4k | Short film | full movie | Sajin | Gopika anil | Achu sugandh
snippet.description:
Pennine Ishtayo - A Musical Short Film | Official Release
"Pennine Ishtayo" is a captivating Malayalam musical short film that explores the deep emotions of love, human connection, and the power of music. Directed by Achu Sugandh and produced by Nithin Thaivalappil under Filmika Cinemas, this film features powerful performances by Sajin Shiva, Gopika Anil, and an ensemble cast of talented actors. With stunning visuals by Rejin Santo and soul-stirring music composed by Bonny Louis, this film is sure to resonate with viewers of all ages.

From the mesmerizing vocals by Sadhika K R, Neethusha A C, Arjun, Nithin K Shiva, and Bonny Louis, to the skillful dance choreography by Surya R K, Pennine Ishtayi is a complete sensory experience that beautifully blends narrative and music.

Key Credits:

Written & Directed by: Achu Sugandh
Produced by: Nithin Thaivalappil, Filmika Cinemas
Cinematography (DoP): Rejin Santo
Music Director: Bonny Louis
Editor: Anandhu S Vijay
Sound Engineer: Aashif Ali
Colorist: Ebin Philip
Mix & Master: Arjun B Nair

Featuring:

Vijaya Sadan
James Parackkal

Episode 4252: Macchar Problem
--------------------------------------------------------
While waiting for the fridges to be transferred, Baagha and Nattu Kaka stay up overnight in Gokuldham Colony, looking after them and battling the mosquito problem.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

अंतरा 1
M - फेंकत अक्षत बिया, बाकी बचत बिया

Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest. Through the lens of sisterhood's enduring bond and the inexorable force of destiny, the narrative unfurls a tapestry of emotions, ultimately celebrating the timeless allure of fate in uniting kindred spirits.
